replyContent: Hi, uninstalling a game doesn't automatically give you a refund from Google Play, though you can request a refund from Google within two hours of purchase by clicking the "Refund" button.  If you wait longer than that, Google doesn't offer that option anymore.  Email us at support@flipline.com and we can check if you're eligible for a refund though
